    "Heart illness, head injuries, high blood pressure, and a lack of exercise are a few of the environmental and lifestyle factors that are linked to an elevated risk of AD (van Praag 2018).",
    "As AD affects the elderly population, their lifestyle, and health gradually deteriorate.",
    "Also, there exists no cure for it.",
    "The disease is primarily managed through supportive care by the healthcare providers.",
    "Thus, its diagnosis at early stages is crucial."
